This documentation describes the Signal Sciences Service Broker for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF). 

PCF Operators install the Signal Sciences Service Broker tile to expose the Signal Science service in the Marketplace. Developers can then integrate Signal Sciences with their apps by embedding the Signal Sciences agent in their app code and binding the service to their app from Apps Manager or the Cloud Foundry Command Line Interface (cf CLI).

## <a id="overview"></a> Overview

Signal Sciences gives you the insights you need to prioritize your security resources to address attacks as they occur. With greater visibility and awareness, you can make informed decisions and confidently run your web applications. Signal Sciences is modern web application security.

Key Features

* Visibility of malicious and anomalous web traffic.
* Protection against malicious traffic that does not disrupt legitimate traffic.
* Integrations with third-party DevOps tools and SIEM solutions.
* Enables visibility and protection over the business risk of applications, e.g. account takeover, high risk transactions, vulnerability discovery, and policy validation.

